%            Maximal formula depth :   11 (   6 average)
%            Number of connectives :   31 (   3 ~  ;   4  |;  14  &)
%                                         (   4 <=>;   6 =>;   0 <=)
%                                         (   0 <~>;   0 ~|;   0 ~&)
%            Number of predicates  :    8 (   0 propositional; 1-2 arity)
%            Number of functors    :    4 (   2 constant; 0-2 arity)
